      "text": "Research how Cline (VS Code extension) stores its AI coding sessions. I need to know:\n1. Where the session data is stored (file path, database location)\n2. What format it uses (SQLite, JSON, JSONL, etc.)\n3. The schema/structure of the session data\n4. What fields are available (messages, tool calls, file edits, timestamps)\n\nSearch the web for \"Cline VS Code session storage format\" and \"Cline AI session data structure\". Also check the Cline GitHub repo for documentation about session storage.\n\nReturn a detailed summary of the storage format, file paths, and schema.",
