trol](/cline/cline/10.3-access-control)\n-   [Authentication and Accounts](/cline/cline/11-authentication-and-accounts)\n-   [Authentication System](/cline/cline/11.1-authentication-system)\n-   [Account Service](/cline/cline/11.2-account-service)\n-   [Credits and Billing](/cline/cline/11.3-credits-and-billing)\n-   [Remote Configuration](/cline/cline/11.4-remote-configuration)\n-   [Banner and Feature Flag Systems](/cline/cline/11.5-banner-and-feature-flag-systems)\n-   [CLI Tool](/cline/cline/12-cli-tool)\n-   [CLI Architecture](/cline/cline/12.1-cli-architecture)\n-   [CLI Commands and Options](/cline/cline/12.2-cli-commands-and-options)\n-   [CLI Interactive Mode](/cline/cline/12.3-cli-interactive-mode)\n-   [CLI Headless Mode](/cline/cline/12.4-cli-headless-mode)\n-   [Agent Client Protocol (ACP)](/cline/cline/12.5-agent-client-protocol-\\(acp\\))\n-   [Cline SDK](/cline/cline/13-cline-sdk)\n-   [SDK Architecture and Packages](/cline/cline/13.1-sdk-architecture-and-packages)\n-   [Agent API and ClineCore](/cline/cline/13.2-agent-api-and-clinecore)\n-   [SDK Provider and Model Gateway](/cline/cline/13.3-sdk-provider-and-model-gateway)\n-   [Plugins and Extensions](/cline/cline/13.4-plugins-and-extensions)\n-   [Hub Daemon and Zen Mode](/cline/cline/13.5-hub-daemon-and-zen-mode)\n-   [Automation and Cron](/cline/cline/13.6-automation-and-cron)\n-   [SDK Examples and Connectors](/cline/cline/13.7-sdk-examples-and-connectors)\n-   [Development and Extensibility](/cline/cline/14-development-and-extensibility)\n-   [Build System and Protocol Buffers](/cline/cline/14.1-build-system-and-protocol-buffers)\n-   [Testing Infrastructure](/cline/cline/14.2-testing-infrastructure)\n-   [Telemetry System](/cline/cline/14.3-telemetry-system)\n-   [Feature Flags](/cline/cline/14.4-feature-flags)\n-   [Publishing and Release](/cline/cline/14.5-publishing-and-release)\n-   [Contributing Guidelines](/cline/cline/14.6-contributing-guidelines)\n-   [Glossary](/cline/cline/15-glossary)\n\nMenu\n\n# Disk Storage Organization\n\nRelevant source files\n\n-   [proto/cline/models.proto](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/proto/cline/models.proto)\n-   [proto/cline/state.proto](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/proto/cline/state.proto)\n-   [src/common.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/common.ts)\n-   [src/core/api/index.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/api/index.ts)\n-   [src/core/commands/reconstructTaskHistory.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/commands/reconstructTaskHistory.ts)\n-   [src/core/context/context-tracking/ContextTrackerTypes.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/context/context-tracking/ContextTrackerTypes.ts)\n-   [src/core/context/context-tracking/FileContextTracker.test.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/context/context-tracking/FileContextTracker.test.ts)\n-   [src/core/context/context-tracking/FileContextTracker.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/context/context-tracking/FileContextTracker.ts)\n-   [src/core/context/context-tracking/ModelContextTracker.test.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/context/context-tracking/ModelContextTracker.test.ts)\n-   [src/core/context/context-tracking/ModelContextTracker.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/context/context-tracking/ModelContextTracker.ts)\n-   [src/core/controller/state/updateSettings.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/controller/state/updateSettings.ts)\n-   [src/core/storage/StateManager.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/StateManager.ts)\n-   [src/core/storage/disk.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts)\n-   [src/core/storage/state-migrations.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/state-migrations.ts)\n-   [src/core/storage/utils/state-helpers.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/utils/state-helpers.ts)\n-   [src/shared/proto-conversions/models/api-configuration-conversion.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/shared/proto-conversions/models/api-configuration-conversion.ts)\n-   [src/shared/storage/state-keys.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/shared/storage/state-keys.ts)\n-   [src/test/cline-api.test.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/test/cline-api.test.ts)\n-   [webview-ui/src/components/settings/sections/FeatureSettingsSection.tsx](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/webview-ui/src/components/settings/sections/FeatureSettingsSection.tsx)\n-   [webview-ui/src/components/settings/sections/TerminalSettingsSection.tsx](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/webview-ui/src/components/settings/sections/TerminalSettingsSection.tsx)\n-   [webview-ui/src/components/settings/utils/providerUtils.ts](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/webview-ui/src/components/settings/utils/providerUtils.ts)\n\nThis page describes how Cline organizes persistent data on disk, including the directory layout for global state, secrets, MCP settings, model caches, and per-task data. It also covers the `GlobalFileNames` constants that define the naming convention for all well-known files.\n\nFor information about the StateManager's in-memory caching and persistence strategy, see page 5.1. For settings precedence rules, see page 5.3.\n\n---\n\n## Storage Architecture Overview\n\nCline uses a multi-tiered storage architecture that combines VS Code's native storage APIs (or CLI equivalents) with direct file system access for structured data and large files. The `StateManager` acts as the central orchestrator, maintaining in-memory caches and coordinating with `StorageContext` to persist data to the appropriate backend.\n\n**Storage Flow and Code Entity Association:**\n\n**Storage Layer Responsibilities:**\n\nLayer\n\nPurpose\n\nRead Pattern\n\nWrite Pattern\n\nPersistence Location\n\nVS Code `globalState`\n\nGlobal settings, provider configs, UI state\n\n`readGlobalStateFromStorage`\n\nDebounced `PERSISTENCE_DELAY_MS`\n\nVS Code SQLite DB\n\nVS Code `workspaceState`\n\nPer-workspace rule/skill toggles\n\n`readWorkspaceStateFromStorage`\n\nDebounced `PERSISTENCE_DELAY_MS`\n\nVS Code SQLite DB\n\nVS Code `secrets`\n\nAPI keys, tokens, OAuth credentials\n\n`readSecretsFromStorage`\n\nDebounced `PERSISTENCE_DELAY_MS`\n\nOS keychain\n\nFile System (tasks)\n\nConversation history, task metadata\n\n`readTaskSettingsFromStorage`\n\n`atomicWriteFile()`\n\n`globalStorageFsPath/tasks/{taskId}/`\n\nFile System (state)\n\nTask history list (`taskHistory.json`)\n\n`readTaskHistoryFromState`\n\n`atomicWriteFile()`\n\n`globalStorageFsPath/state/`\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/storage/StateManager.ts58-113](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/StateManager.ts#L58-L113) [src/core/storage/utils/state-helpers.ts22-86](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/utils/state-helpers.ts#L22-L86) [src/core/storage/disk.ts30-42](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L30-L42) [src/core/storage/disk.ts21-29](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L21-L29)\n\n---\n\n## Global Storage Organization\n\nCline maintains a centralized home directory for configuration that persists across different IDE installations (VS Code, JetBrains, CLI).\n\n### Cline Home Path\n\nThe primary cross-platform home directory is `~/.cline`. This directory is intended to house global configurations, global skills, and provider-specific model caches.\n\n-   **macOS**: `/Users/username/.cline`\n-   **Linux**: `/home/username/.cline`\n-   **Windows**: `C:\\Users\\username\\.cline`\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/storage/disk.ts117-119](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L117-L119) [src/core/storage/disk.ts172-174](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L172-L174)\n\n### Well-Known Global Files (`GlobalFileNames`)\n\nThe `GlobalFileNames` constant in `src/core/storage/disk.ts` defines the names for shared configuration and cache files.\n\nConstant\n\nFilename\n\nPurpose\n\n`apiConversationHistory`\n\n`api_conversation_history.json`\n\nRaw conversation history for API calls.\n\n`uiMessages`\n\n`ui_messages.json`\n\nMessage history formatted for the Webview UI.\n\n`mcpSettings`\n\n`cline_mcp_settings.json`\n\nConfiguration for MCP servers.\n\n`clineModels`\n\n`cline_models.json`\n\nCached list of models from the Cline provider.\n\n`openRouterModels`\n\n`openrouter_models.json`\n\nCached list of models from OpenRouter.\n\n`vercelAiGatewayModels`\n\n`vercel_ai_gateway_models.json`\n\nCached list of models from Vercel AI Gateway.\n\n`mcpMarketplaceCatalog`\n\n`mcp_marketplace_catalog.json`\n\nCatalog of available MCP servers.\n\n`remoteConfig`\n\n`remote_config_{orgId}.json`\n\nEnterprise remote configuration for a specific organization.\n\n`clineRules`\n\n`.clinerules`\n\nGlobal rules for agent behavior.\n\n`workflows`\n\n`.clinerules/workflows`\n\nDirectory for global workflow definitions.\n\n`hooksDir`\n\n`.clinerules/hooks`\n\nDirectory for global tool and lifecycle hooks.\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/storage/disk.ts44-70](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L44-L70)\n\n---\n\n## Per-Task Storage Organization\n\nEach task initiated in Cline is assigned a unique ID (typically a ULID) and has its own isolated storage directory under the global storage path.\n\n### Task Directory Layout\n\nWhen a task is created, `ensureTaskDirectoryExists(taskId)` creates a subdirectory within the `tasks` folder of the extension's global storage.\n\n-   **`api_conversation_history.json`**: Stores the raw message history (`ClineStorageMessage[]`) used for LLM context. [src/core/storage/disk.ts45](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L45-L45)\n-   **`ui_messages.json`**: Stores the `ClineMessage` array used to reconstruct the chat UI. [src/core/storage/disk.ts47](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L47-L47)\n-   **`task_metadata.json`**: Contains `TaskMetadata` which tracks `files_in_context`, `model_usage`, and `environment_history`. [src/core/storage/disk.ts67](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L67-L67)\n-   **`context_history.json`**: Tracks the evolution of context mentions throughout the task. [src/core/storage/disk.ts46](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L46-L46)\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/storage/disk.ts44-70](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L44-L70) [src/core/storage/disk.ts121-123](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L121-L123) [src/core/context/context-tracking/ContextTrackerTypes.ts1-10](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/context/context-tracking/ContextTrackerTypes.ts#L1-L10)\n\n### File Context Tracking\n\nThe `FileContextTracker` manages task-specific metadata to prevent stale context. It monitors files that have been read or edited by Cline and uses `chokidar` to detect external modifications.\n\n-   **`files_in_context`**: An array of `FileMetadataEntry` in `task_metadata.json`.\n-   **State Tracking**: Entries track the last known hash and modification time to determine if context needs refreshing.\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/context/context-tracking/FileContextTracker.ts108-163](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/context/context-tracking/FileContextTracker.ts#L108-L163) [src/core/context/context-tracking/FileContextTracker.ts25-37](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/context/context-tracking/FileContextTracker.ts#L25-L37)\n\n### Atomic Persistence\n\nTo ensure data integrity, Cline uses an atomic write pattern in `atomicWriteFile`. It writes data to a `.tmp` file with a timestamp and random suffix before renaming it to the target path using `fs.rename`.\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/storage/disk.ts30-42](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L30-L42)\n\n---\n\n## Persistence of Sensitive Data (Secrets)\n\nCline uses the VS Code `SecretStorage` API (backed by the OS keychain) or the CLI equivalent to store sensitive credentials. These are managed by `StateManager` via `SecretKeys`.\n\n### Key Secret Identifiers\n\nThe `SecretKeys` array in `state-keys.ts` defines the fields stored in secure storage, including:\n\n-   `apiKey`: Primary Anthropic API key.\n-   `openRouterApiKey`: Key for OpenRouter.\n-   `awsAccessKey`, `awsSecretKey`, `awsSessionToken`: Credentials for AWS Bedrock.\n-   `geminiApiKey`, `deepSeekApiKey`, `openAiApiKey`, `openAiNativeApiKey`: Provider-specific keys.\n-   `clineApiKey`: Key for the Cline managed service.\n-   `mcpOAuthSecrets`: JSON string containing OAuth tokens for MCP servers.\n\n**Sources:** [src/shared/storage/state-keys.ts12-14](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/shared/storage/state-keys.ts#L12-L14) [proto/cline/state.proto62-109](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/proto/cline/state.proto#L62-L109) [src/core/storage/StateManager.ts65](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/StateManager.ts#L65-L65)\n\n---\n\n## Model Cache Organization\n\nTo improve performance and support offline model selection, Cline caches model metadata from various providers in-memory and on disk.\n\n### Cache Implementation\n\nDynamic model information is stored in the `StateManager.modelInfoCache`. While some providers are purely in-memory, others persist to disk using `GlobalFileNames`.\n\n-   **OpenRouter**: Cached in `openrouter_models.json`.\n-   **Cline**: Cached in `cline_models.json`.\n-   **Vercel AI Gateway**: Cached in `vercel_ai_gateway_models.json`.\n-   **Groq/Baseten/Hicap/HuaweiCloudMaas**: Persisted to respective JSON files.\n\nThe cache has a TTL defined by `MODEL_CACHE_TTL_MS` (default 1 hour) to balance responsiveness with up-to-date model data.\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/storage/StateManager.ts75-104](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/StateManager.ts#L75-L104) [src/core/storage/disk.ts44-55](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L44-L55)\n\n---\n\n## Migration and Directory Management\n\nCline includes logic to ensure required directories exist and to migrate legacy data from previous versions.\n\n### Directory Management Functions\n\n-   `ensureTaskDirectoryExists(taskId)`: Creates the isolated task folder. [src/core/storage/disk.ts121-123](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L121-L123)\n-   `ensureMcpServersDirectoryExists()`: Creates `~/Documents/Cline/MCP`. [src/core/storage/disk.ts147-156](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L147-L156)\n-   `ensureRulesDirectoryExists()`: Creates `~/Documents/Cline/Rules`. [src/core/storage/disk.ts125-134](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L125-L134)\n-   `ensureWorkflowsDirectoryExists()`: Creates `~/Documents/Cline/Workflows`. [src/core/storage/disk.ts136-145](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L136-L145)\n-   `ensureHooksDirectoryExists()`: Creates `~/Documents/Cline/Hooks`. [src/core/storage/disk.ts158-167](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L158-L167)\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/storage/disk.ts121-167](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/disk.ts#L121-L167)\n\n### Storage Migrations\n\nThe extension handles several migration paths in `src/core/storage/state-migrations.ts` (Note: Implementation details for migrations are handled during extension activation or `StateManager.initialize`).\n\n**Sources:** [src/core/storage/StateManager.ts128-161](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/core/storage/StateManager.ts#L128-L161) [src/common.ts45-53](https://github.com/cline/cline/blob/8a6441fd/src/common.ts#L45-L53)\n\nDismiss\n\nRefresh this wiki\n\nEnter email to refresh\n\n### On this page\n\n-   [Disk Storage Organization](#disk-storage-organization)\n-   [Storage Architecture Overview](#storage-architecture-overview)\n-   [Global Storage Organization](#global-storage-organization)\n-   [Cline Home Path](#cline-home-path)\n-   [Well-Known Global Files (\\`GlobalFileNames\\`)](#well-known-global-files-globalfilenames)\n-   [Per-Task Storage Organization](#per-task-storage-organization)\n-   [Task Directory Layout](#task-directory-layout)\n-   [File Context Tracking](#file-context-tracking)\n-   [Atomic Persistence](#atomic-persistence)\n-   [Persistence of Sensitive Data (Secrets)](#persistence-of-sensitive-data-secrets)\n-   [Key Secret Identifiers](#key-secret-identifiers)\n-   [Model Cache Organization](#model-cache-organization)\n-   [Cache Implementation](#cache-implementation)\n-   [Migration and Directory Management](#migration-and-directory-management)\n-   [Directory Management Functions](#directory-management-functions)\n-   [Storage Migrations](#storage-migrations)",
